                                          "name": "The answer makes several time-bounded periodizatio",
                                          "fill": "#111111ff",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": 380,
                                          "content": "The answer makes several time-bounded periodizations: The Jam era, The Style Council era, early solo/1990s, acoustic-focused early 2000s, and later solo work from 2008 onward.",
